OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPartly
OL,6,Fcloudy this evening and dry for most,
OL,7,Fhowever a few lingering showers will
OL,8,Fgradually clear away to leave the rest
OL,9,Fof the night dry with clear spells.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FA dry, bright morning with
OL,12,Fhazy sunny spells. More in the way of
OL,13,Fcloud in the afternoon and few
OL,14,Fshowers, one or two of these on the
OL,15,Fheavy side.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FA good
OL,18,Fdeal of dry weather during this period
OL,19,Fwith variable amounts of cloud.
OL,20,FHowever a few showers or spells of
OL,21,Frain can't be ruled out.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
